"Employment Support  Service for PWDs > Personal Assistance Service | KEAD\nGo to main content\nThis program is aimed at supporting the employment of workers with severe impairments by\r\n        raising their workplace adaptability with the aid of personal assistants who are dispatched for set periods.\nPersonal Assistance Services\npersonal Assistance service provision : service type and how to assist\nservice type\nhow to assist\nPhysical, Brain lesion\nAssisting in minor job duties such as filing papers and commute to work\nVisual\nAssisting in document reading, web search\nHearing\nAssisting in sign language interpretation, recording conversation, and talking phone calls\nIntellectual, Developemental\nAssisting in communication, coustomer service\nOthers\nAssisting in tasks considered to be necessary after evaluation"